Description.Name: Basic Attack: High-Pressure Flamethrower
Description.Desc:
Press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> to activate:
Unleashes up to 5 attacks in front, followed by a powerful flaming blade strike, dealing <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color> and <color=#FF5521>Fire DMG</color>.

Description.Name: Dodge: Dancing Flames
Description.Desc:
Press <IconMap:Icon_Evade> to activate:
A quick dash dodge.
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

Description.Name: Dash Attack: Assault Command
Description.Desc:
Press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> during a dodge to activate:
Perform a quick forward attack, dealing <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color>.

Description.Name: Dodge Counter: Counter Opportunity
Description.Desc:
Press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> during a <color=#FFFFFF>Perfect Dodge</color> to activate:
Launch a series of attacks on enemies in front, dealing <color=#F0D12B>Physical DMG</color> and <color=#FF5521>Fire DMG</color>.
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

Description.Name: Special Attack: Burning Spirit
Special Attack: Flash of Corrosion
EX Special Attack: Watch Your Step
EX Special Attack: Crimson Vortex
EX Special Attack: Heat Charge
EX Special Attack: Blazing Burst
EX Special Attack: Watch Your Step
Chain Attack: Overheated Barrel
Ultimate: Dance With Fire
Quick Assist: Searing Slash
Defensive Assist: Blazing Gunblade
Description.Desc:
When the on-field character is about to be attacked, press <IconMap:Icon_Switch> to activate:
Parries the enemy's attack, accumulating massive Daze.
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

Description.Name: Assist Follow-Up: Boiling Pierce
Description.Desc:
Press <IconMap:Icon_Normal> after a <color=#FFFFFF>Defensive Assist</color> to activate:
Perform multiple attacks on enemies in front, dealing <color=#FF5521>Fire DMG</color>.
Character is invulnerable while using this skill.

1.Name: Luxury Cat House
1.Desc: Orphie & Magus's [Special Attack: Flash of Corrosion], [EX Special Attack: Crimson Vortex], [EX Special Attack: Heat Charge], [EX Special Attack: Blazing Burst] ignore 15% of target's <color=#FF5521>Fire RES</color>, and Agents with [Zeroed In] deal 20% more DMG.

2.Name: Weird Food List
2.Desc: When Orphie & Magus triggers [Aftershock], restore 65 Decibels. This effect can trigger once every 4 seconds. After using [Ultimate], increases CRIT DMG dealt by their skills by 40% for up to 30 seconds.

4.Name: Pink Holster
4.Desc: Initial duration of [Zeroed In] is increased to 18 seconds, and Orphie & Magus's [EX Special Attack: Heat Charge] or [Ultimate: Dance with Fire] deals 45% more DMG.

6.Name: Magic Seed
6.Desc: With enough energy, after the blade attack of [Basic Attack: High-Pressure Flamethrower], press <IconMap:Icon_SpecialReady> to immediately follow up with [EX Special Attack: Crimson Vortex]; When the blade attack of [Basic Attack: High-Pressure Flamethrower] is activated, recover 10 points of [Bottled Heat], and the Interrupt Level during the low-power phase of [EX Special Attack: Heat Charge] will also increase; When the laser from [EX Special Attack: Heat Charge] or [Ultimate] hits enemies, it deals additional <color=#FF5521>Fire DMG</color> equal to 360% of Orphie & Magus's ATK. This effect can be triggered once every 0.5 seconds and is considered as [EX Special Attack] and [Aftershock] DMG.
